{
  "text": "Arguably, PR algorithms based on deep learning [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] can accommodate new data by simply appending it to the dataset and fine-tuning the network parameters. However, as we will show later, this fine-tuning process is still too costly to be practical, and the lack of accurate labels in the testing sequence can be a major obstacle.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "4547677",
